race.comment: ZIPPING O'REILLY (1) has been beaten for early speed lately, last time finishing fourth (28.25) in a Grade 5 at Horsham. Can bounce back. MANDOLIN STORM (3) has a moderate overall strike-rate. Finished in the minors latest when third (25.68) at this track and may be close to breaking through. Can measure up. WALK WITH PRIDE (2) goes very well at the distance with three wins and a placing from seven starts. Hit the frame latest (26.18) when second at Geelong in a Grade 5. Looks a key chance on best figures. IT'S BUBBLE TIME (8) comes into calculations after placing most recently.
